headline: NextEra Energy beats earnings estimates despite revenue miss
summary: Investing.com -- NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE:NEE) reported third-quarter adjusted earnings of $1.13 per share, exceeding analyst expectations of $1.02, while revenue came in at $7.97 billion, below the $8.17 billion consensus. The companyâ€™s shares rose 1.7% following the announcement.
